title: Highschool DXD Born Season 3 English Dub
description:
This is the English Dub of Highschool DXD Born also known as Season 3. It has no subtitles, and includes all 12 episodes from season 3. 


I couldn't find a torrent anywhere, so I found a site that was still hosting it for viewing and ripped it from them. It's good quality, not a bluray or anything, but if you're as desperate as I was you won't care.

Please keep in mind I'm hosting this by myself to start on a 20 Mb/s up connection. So, please remember:


*********************************Seed Till You Bleed*********************************
